{"tid":1593334,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"抗爭新戰線: 全民公民教育, 入黎brain storm","createTime":"2019-09-25T04:28:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T04:59:24.000Z","uid":297616,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ebcd4aed1ea2750d5f3b127f690ca468543c021b","tid":1593334,"uid":297616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:28:28.000Z","msg":"鬼佬教授︰你地曾經很多攻勢，但為什麼現在只沉迷每週和警察打鬥？<br />\n<br />\n瞓瞓下諗到答案: <strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全民公民教育</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">大家問心有幾認識香港既制度暴力?</span></strong></span><br />\n即係立法會點解被閹  (keyword: 行政主導, 議員提唔到法案，分組點票, 功能組別。。。)<br />\n<br />\n我諗好大部分人都唔知咩黎，or聽過唔記得左要溫返書, 咁不如搞全民公民教育, 了解下香港既<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">政制不公</span></span>, 咁爭取雙普選都名正言順d<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">有咩可以搞? </span><br />\n遍地開花放映會, <br />\n街頭流動公民教室,<br />\n youtube動畫? <br />\n 民建聯賣港實錄 documentary?<br />\n 立法會投票紀錄解構? (搵返曬d被功能組別否決既民生法案)?<br />\n區議會提款機案例?<br />\n大家一齊諗下<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>全力宣傳下政府同d 建制派做過既仆街野</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"7bb5c24a23b22d23d7e2237a5e0dd541ac9aed87","tid":1593334,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:28:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592119</a>"},{"pid":"581d589cd2526284ba9012dc3e714cef1be0baef","tid":1593334,"uid":297616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T04:59:24.000Z","msg":"自推1"}]}